New Brew On The Block! From redefining café spaces to putting Black ownership front and center, these innovators are changing the way we experience coffee with new #BlackOwned coffee brand Tāst. ☕️⁠
⁠
"For us, coffee isn’t just a noun, it’s a verb. ‘Coffeeing’ means to care honestly, loudly, and openly. When you see two Black men on the street giving each other dap, that’s ‘coffeeing’…We have to figure out how to actively care for our customers.” - Jason Reynolds⁠
⁠
